{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4288","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4288/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4288/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4288/events","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4288","id":17550004,"number":4288,"title":"upload files not working on shared server (mediatemple)","user":{"login":"zoneblaze","id":684079,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/6ba5e5b8581601f11367cd8eb071e575?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fcd6a27a72326dccb5769d596a0357421.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"6ba5e5b8581601f11367cd8eb071e575","url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze","html_url":"https://github.com/zoneblaze","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zoneblaze/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","assignee":null,"milestone":null,"comments":10,"created_at":"2013-08-02t08:41:16z","updated_at":"2013-09-07t15:07:42z","closed_at":"2013-08-03t14:03:36z","pull_request":{"html_url":null,"diff_url":null,"patch_url":null},"body":"i've installed owncloud on the mediatemple. and noticed uploading files does not work on their type of grid shared server. i think the free_space function fails as it tries to access out of scope values. but i'm not a php person really.\r\n\r\ncurrently the solution seems to be to edit local.php and hardcode a value, that is what i did to make it work:\r\n\r\npublic function free_space($path) {\r\n  //return @disk_free_space($this->datadir.$path);\r\n  return 2147483648; // 2gb\r\n}\r\n\r\nalso had to make sure .htaccess maxsize values in the root folder are higher than the .htaccess values in the cloud root folder as well as the php.ini file\r\n\r\n.htaccess:\r\nphp_value upload_max_filesize 620m\r\nphp_value post_max_size 620m\r\nphp_value memory_limit 620m\r\n\r\nphp.ini:\r\n; increase maximum post size\r\nupload_max_filesize = 700m\r\npost_max_size = 700m\r\nmemory_limit = 700m\r\n\r\nby the way, setting up php zip on mediatemple was a nightmare for a backend amateur like myself. i'm more of a front end designer/coder type ; )\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"mtgap","id":1097106,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/454a73ee5feeb428d0c163a48903332c?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f52d29a66f285a1d61125dd69ac0766b2.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"454a73ee5feeb428d0c163a48903332c","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap","html_url":"https://github.com/mtgap","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}